one_reviews_text:
Tried playing deuces wild. The developer does realize that 2 deuces and a pair is 4 of a kind right? Game doesn't reconize when more than 1 deuce is in play. I haven't tried the other games yet but I can assume they are likely broken as well.

I'll update review if they can fix this simple issues.

If this game isn't being updated anymore, Oculus should pull it from the store.

review_title: Fun way to waste a little time
one_reviews_text: Fun game for a few dollars. Wish the poker games were Game King along with the official sounds. Tactile Feedback could be a lot better. Looking forward to future versions.

review_title: 2.3 GB for ONE measly Video Poker
one_reviews_text: Why only one machine? It's just boring as all get out
review_feedback: Hi just letting you know I slimmed down the game and released the update with 5 more game modes.  Thanks for your feedback and patience!  :)
